                            <comment id="13414547" author="tlipcon" created="Sat, 14 Jul 2012 23:39:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Good idea to log this. Is there any reasonably easy way to get at the connecting peer&apos;s IP address through our layers of wrapped transports? It would be much nicer to include this, to help debug these issues from the server side. But if it&apos;s not possible, I&apos;m +1 on the patch as it is.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
